{"tid":1951670,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國國民共赴國難，追責中共新“八國聯軍”呼之欲出","createTime":"2020-03-31T06:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T08:30:38.000Z","uid":202577,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a05bec9c1be218d9f403ea69970be8b3d0c1c4","tid":1951670,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OxRj27kTWN0&amp;t=15s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOxRj27kTWN0%26t%3D15s&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=d282b6cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OxRj27kTWN0&amp;t=15s</a>"},{"pid":"5b0b25d99008cb21872dffb880db9d2c19cca018","tid":1951670,"uid":202577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"老侵3月23號改口唔再用中國病毒，第二日就有兩個共和黨議員係國會提出向中共索償議案，可見特朗普之前故意引導輿論爭端，刺激令國會入面反共力量接手做野，然後自己就立即鬆人。<br />\n<br />\n係美國對台灣轉向方面，特朗普都扮演同樣角色。佢當選後立即打電話比蔡英文，惹黎一d爭議，令國會入面親臺力量開始做野，然後自己就扮無事繼續同北京談判。而家美國挺臺策略已經落實。<br />\n<br />\n單獨由美國向中共追責同索償，力量唔足夠，目前看黎，有可能加入係日本英國。<br />\n<br />\n中共很可能堅決拒絕賠償同調差，但發達國家唔見得會真係&ldquo;打&rdquo;佢。<br />\n<br />\n自從2008年金融危機後，世界出現逆全球化發展，將來會持續下去。呢次疫情後，發達國家同中共脫鉤可能性增大，中國閉關鎖國機會增加，人民受苦。<br />\n<br />\n根據過去經驗，如果市民越多參與改革，過程就越少痛苦。"},{"pid":"2e69594e1f3c612ea00d7d13fb098bcd3cd404a4","tid":1951670,"uid":202577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"紐約有1000名退休醫護自發地重回前線，民主國家唔需要好似某強國咁成日維穩，但國家有難時自然有唔少人出黎做野。<br />\n<br />\n極權國家嚴重低估了民眾本身動員能力。一戰期間，當美國宣佈參戰時，陸軍只有12萬人（人口7千萬），但宣戰兩個月後就950萬人登記參軍。<br />\n<br />\n美國對人民 &ldquo;洗腦&rdquo;方法：對人民誠實、尊重、讓人民感受到自己是國家主人。"},{"pid":"720ee4f3b2e7cd207baf058b83433023153ffa71","tid":1951670,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4cd8c6b47589415e6a7628ad6c344baa7ae32f51","tid":1951670,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d1d92132d9897e7421cf611239bad9c1d07035d4","tid":1951670,"uid":304856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:44:30.000Z","msg":"Uncle Sam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解美國自己一個唔夠做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國一個人挑俄國+中國+北韓都遊刃有餘喎🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸。只不過人地係民主國家，唔可以濫權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（要理民眾肯唔肯打）"},{"pid":"c1b4439361b374b39853878d7b67d0da2d4b6ed7","tid":1951670,"uid":202577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1d92132d9897e7421cf611239bad9c1d07035d4","tid":1951670,"uid":304856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:44:30.000Z","msg":"Uncle Sam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解美國自己一個唔夠做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國一個人挑俄國+中國+北韓都遊刃有餘喎🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸。只不過人地係民主國家，唔可以濫權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（要理民眾肯唔肯打）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:45:59.000Z","msg":"除非中共發動戰爭，如果唔係美國無乜可能/需要打仗<br />\n脫鉤+制裁可以好傷<br />\n諗下無咗外國資金、市場、技術，中共會點"},{"pid":"daef81152d7d143cf960c1e70410b33f265a7143","tid":1951670,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"花你少少時間同位置<br />\n希望你賞面睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">超合作？預期性服從？公民不合作與管治成本。</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1951717</a>"},{"pid":"760812f33b337ee5fba279f1bd2aa3709ed2a7eb","tid":1951670,"